data.title: Missy Elliott's Hottest Collaborations - [site:name]
data.meta_description: Relive some of Missy's hottest collaborations!
data.text:
Hip-Hop legend, Missy Elliott ALWAYS brings the heat…even when it’s not her song! Her signature flow, undeniable swag, and impeccable musical production skills can make a hit out of any song. Her newest collabo? “BURNITUP!” with the legendary Janet Jackson. Check out our list, and relive some of Missy’s hottest collaborations.

BURNITUP! – Janet Jackson ft. Missy Elliott

Make It Hot – Nicole Wray ft. Missy Elliott

Ladies Night – Lil Kim, Angie Martinez, Left Eye, Da Brat & Missy Elliott

Let It Go – Keyshia Cole ft. Missy Elliott & Lil’ Kim

Signs – Beyoncé ft. Missy Elliott

Whatcha Think About That – Pussycat Dolls ft. Missy Elliott

Oops Oh My – Tweet ft. Missy Elliott

Nobody’s Perfect – J. Cole ft. Missy Eliott

Lady Marmalade – Christina Aguilera, Lil’ Kim, Mya, Missy Elliott, Pink

One, Two Step – Ciara ft. Missy Elliott

Without Me – Fantasia ft. Kelly Rowland & Missy Elliott

What’s your favorite Missy collab? Let us know on Twitter.
